  -rsstail-1.3.ebuild, -rsstail-1.4.ebuild:
  Remove old.

  08 Mar 2012; Pawel Hajdan jr <phajdan.jr@gentoo.org> rsstail-1.8.ebuild:
  x86 stable wrt bug #400455

  24 Feb 2012; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> rsstail-1.8.ebuild:
  Stable for amd64, wrt bug #400455

*rsstail-1.8 (26 Sep 2011)

  26 Sep 2011; Tim Harder <radhermit@gentoo.org> +rsstail-1.8.ebuild:
  Version bump. Update to EAPI 4.

  22 May 2008; Markus Meier <maekke@gentoo.org> rsstail-1.3.ebuild:
  x86 stable, bug #223143

  21 May 2008; Robert Buchholz <rbu@gentoo.org> rsstail-1.3.ebuild:
  amd64 stable, bug #223143

*rsstail-1.4 (21 May 2008)

  21 May 2008; Robert Buchholz <rbu@gentoo.org> +rsstail-1.4.ebuild:
  Version bump: "numerous enhancements, made its output more configurable"

  28 Apr 2008; Christian Heim <phreak@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Remove Wulf C. Krueger (philantrop) from metadata.xml (as per #168573).

  26 Aug 2007; Andrej Kacian <ticho@gentoo.org> rsstail-1.0.ebuild:
  Stable on x86, bug #190252.

  25 Aug 2007; Wulf C. Krueger <philantrop@gentoo.org> rsstail-1.0.ebuild:
  Marked stable on amd64 as per bug 190252.

*rsstail-1.3 (25 Aug 2007)

  25 Aug 2007; Wulf C. Krueger <philantrop@gentoo.org> +rsstail-1.3.ebuild:
  Version bump to 1.3 as requested by rbu.
  Upstream changes:
  - added switch that limits the amount of text displayed
  - added switch which prevents rsstail from aborting when an error occurs
  - fixed segfault on FreeBSD
  - man page added

*rsstail-1.0 (19 Apr 2007)

